data.title: Vintage Roland TR-808 Rim Shot sound
data.meta_description: Hi, while building my own set of analog drum models, I've found a lot of synthesized kicks, snares, claps, toms, also some cymbals but the 808 rim shot seems to be a rarity.
data.text:
Audiobus: Use your music apps together.

What is Audiobus? — Audiobus is an award-winning music app for iPhone and iPad which lets you use your other music apps together. Chain effects on your favourite synth, run the output of apps or Audio Units into an app like GarageBand or Loopy, or select a different audio interface output for each app. Route MIDI between apps — drive a synth from a MIDI sequencer, or add an arpeggiator to your MIDI keyboard — or sync with your external MIDI gear. And control your entire setup from a MIDI controller.

Download on the App Store
